{"tid":2382504,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"阿嬌演妲己Cool爆滲氣質　網民有讚冇彈","createTime":"2021-01-27T10:17:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T21:59:19.000Z","uid":262131,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"5f1a45d8d65e32ebaa3ea638a40f30ae71a94893","tid":2382504,"uid":262131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T10:17:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gT4KGGY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgT4KGGY.jpg&h=1b27c5fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UFE6U1X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUFE6U1X.jpg&h=63d56f0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8G6dz1W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8G6dz1W.jpg&h=911434e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gKyLq8A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgKyLq8A.jpg&h=ea0ec16b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日前40歲生日嘅鍾欣潼（阿嬌）早前同拍攝大陸電影《封神之妖狐王妃》，飾演蘇妲己，而男主角係扮演霸氣帝王嘅沈震軒，兩人有不少對手戲，劇照終於出爐，阿嬌嘅造型令網民讚嘆美若天仙，連沈震軒都留言大讚「超美妲己」！<br />\n<br />\n一直被指身形反覆嘅阿嬌，喺戲中盡展氣質，着上戲服策騎，有型又靚，下巴尖尖輪廓凸出，果然係360無死角美女，網上評論都係一面倒有讚冇彈呀，更封佢做「最美妲己」！而佢呢個Look，不禁令人諗起佢喺2002年於《齊天大聖孫悟空》扮演紫薇仙子嘅造型，即使已相隔19年，但阿嬌依然冇走樣，零歲月痕迹，一樣咁青春可人呀！"},{"pid":"635332c2e7577883c81ae342d0a1089ec7423533","tid":2382504,"uid":242537,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T10:22:15.000Z","msg":"狂徒：<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6a745a10443547afea2f6aadfa17281742b8b15","tid":2382504,"uid":192726,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T10:27:42.000Z","msg":"明眼人一睇就知係移花接木 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/an